  "title": "Field Sampling Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Key roles and responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Site sampling and testing of Indoor Air Quality &amp; Industrial Hygiene Air Monitoring test in various industries</li>\n  <li>Perform maintenance, troubleshooting &amp; calibration of sampling equipment</li>\n  <li>Ensure proper documentation and records updating at the end of each working day</li>\n  <li>Generate reports including evaluation, discussion and reporting of the test results to clients</li>\n  <li>Ensure safety and adhere to all Safe Work Procedures</li>\n  <li>Ad-hoc duties assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Skills &amp; Experience</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in ITE/NITEC qualification or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Excel, Word and Outlook</li>\n  <li>Training will be provided</li>\n  <li>Able to write &amp; communicate in English</li>\n  <li>Self-driven, team player with initiative, willingness to learn and good communication skills</li>\n  <li>Able to work in a fast-paced working environment, and able to multi-task.</li>\n  <li>Must be able to commit OT</li>\n  <li><strong>Possess a valid Singapore Class 3 driving license</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Basic + OT + Driving Allowance</li>\n  <li>Annual variable bonus (performance base)</li>\n  <li>Medical benefit</li>\n  <li>Career development plan through continuous and structured training program</li>\n</ul>",
